---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - spike.land"
  description="spike.land privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="bg-background text-foreground font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <nav class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-border">
      <a href="/" class="font-display font-bold text-xl tracking-tight hover:text-primary transition-colors">spike.land</a>
      <div class="flex gap-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        <a href="/pricing" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Pricing</a>
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Blog</a>
      </div>
      <a href="/login" class="bg-foreground text-background px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        Get Started
      </a>
    </nav>

    <main class="flex-1 max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-24 space-y-12">
      <header class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-black tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-6 text-foreground/90 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold">What we collect</h2>
          <p>When you use spike.land we collect basic account information (name, email, OAuth profile) and anonymous usage analytics (page views, feature usage). We do not sell your data to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold">Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and optional analytics cookies to understand how the platform is used. You can decline analytics cookies via the banner shown on your first visit.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold">Data storage</h2>
          <p>Your data is stored on Cloudflare infrastructure (Workers, D1, R2) within their global network. We retain account data for as long as your account is active.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold">Your rights</h2>
          <p>You can request a copy of your data or ask us to delete your account at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:hello@spike.land" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@spike.land</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold">Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related questions, reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@spike.land" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@spike.land</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-border py-8 text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      <span>&copy; 2026 spike.land. All rights reserved.</span>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
